    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe concept of \"relative position\" is useful in many contexts for plugins to place / position things. (Examples: `vim.ui.img`, `vim.lsp.util.make_floating_popup_options`)\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nProvide `vim.pos.rel(kind:'cursor'|'editor'|'laststatus'|'mouse'|'tabline'|'win')`.\n\nImplementation note: extract the internals of `nvim_open_win(…,{relative=…})` ?",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
