        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@justinmk vim.opt.relativenumber exists, but this is only for cursor. What exactly are you looking for? Are you looking for an enhance of vim.opt.relativenumber? If so what is the expected behaviour of all the rest of the options excluding cursor?",
